videos.description: Donta Hall secures an offensive rebound and drops in the put back surrounded by multiple defenders for the Tide.
videos.headline: Alabama's Hall owns the paint

videos.description: Donta Hall gets a nice pass from Braxton Key and finishes strong with the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Alabama's Hall throws down monster slam

videos.description: Collin Sexton lulls his defender to sleep with the dribble and the n knocks down a 3-pointer in his face.
videos.headline: Alabama's Sexton drills corner 3

videos.description: Collin Sexton draws some oohs and ahhs from the crowd on his way to the hoop for the Tide in the second half.
videos.headline: Alabama's Sexton attacks rim with nifty move

videos.description: Herbert Jones drives into the lane and dishes to Donta Hall who finishes strong in the second half.
videos.headline: Alabama's Hall stuffs home slam

videos.description: Donta Hall receives a lob  from half court and tips in the basket with a defender all over him.
videos.headline: Alabama's Hall cant not be stopped
